56
00:05:00,800 --> 00:05:01,840
What are you doing?

57
00:05:02,200 --> 00:05:03,320
It's so hard.

58
00:05:03,320 --> 00:05:04,440
I don't even like it.

59
00:05:04,560 --> 00:05:05,080
You—

60
00:05:05,320 --> 00:05:06,080
How dare you!

61
00:05:06,440 --> 00:05:07,920
What do you mean, "you"?

62
00:05:08,840 --> 00:05:09,960
I just want to know

63
00:05:10,360 --> 00:05:12,160
what the city lord usually does.

64
00:05:12,720 --> 00:05:14,680
You really have no regard for proper manners.

65
00:05:16,440 --> 00:05:18,480
How am I not being proper?

66
00:05:19,680 --> 00:05:21,200
You completely ignore me.

67
00:05:21,200 --> 00:05:22,200
You don't even look at me.

68
00:05:22,200 --> 00:05:23,040
Tell me,

69
00:05:23,040 --> 00:05:24,960
isn't that being rude?

70
00:05:26,960 --> 00:05:28,360
No one has ever dared speak to me like this.

71
00:05:28,440 --> 00:05:29,680
You're the first.

72
00:05:30,200 --> 00:05:30,840
Fine.

73
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:32,680
I'll stay right here

74
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:35,280
and listen to what you have to say.

75
00:05:35,440 --> 00:05:37,480
Let's see how you interpret the "Lessons for Women."

76
00:05:39,600 --> 00:05:41,840
My understanding of the "Lessons for Women" is

77
00:05:42,840 --> 00:05:44,440
that women here

78
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:47,160
live such miserable lives.

79
00:05:47,960 --> 00:05:48,680
Miserable?

80
00:05:48,840 --> 00:05:49,360
Yeah.

81
00:05:50,800 --> 00:05:52,840
Doesn't the book say

82
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:56,320
that women should always be humble and yielding,

83
00:05:56,680 --> 00:05:58,960
put others before themselves,

84
00:05:59,200 --> 00:06:00,080
and ideally,

85
00:06:00,080 --> 00:06:01,320
be even more hardworking,

86
00:06:01,440 --> 00:06:02,720
working all day long?

87
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:04,560
What else?

88
00:06:04,600 --> 00:06:05,680
Take care of themselves,

89
00:06:05,720 --> 00:06:06,360
and if there's nothing to do,

90
00:06:06,360 --> 00:06:07,280
go out less and play less.

91
00:06:07,560 --> 00:06:08,440
Whenever something happens,

92
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:10,480
they should always put their husband first.

93
00:06:10,560 --> 00:06:11,080
Tell me,

94
00:06:11,320 --> 00:06:13,280
isn't that just too miserable?

95
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:16,920
Then if it's like you said,

96
00:06:17,320 --> 00:06:19,720
that a woman living for her husband is miserable,

97
00:06:20,440 --> 00:06:21,200
then

98
00:06:21,440 --> 00:06:23,080
what would not be miserable?

99
00:06:24,960 --> 00:06:26,280
I think

100
00:06:26,560 --> 00:06:28,680
men and women

101
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:30,040
should be equal.

102
00:06:30,200 --> 00:06:32,040
We all have the right to pursue our dreams.

103
00:06:32,080 --> 00:06:34,280
Everyone should have their own hobbies.

104
00:06:34,320 --> 00:06:36,560
Why revolve around men every day?

105
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:37,320
It's boring.

106
00:06:37,840 --> 00:06:38,960
How meaningless.

107
00:06:41,280 --> 00:06:42,680
So you love when you want to love,

108
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:43,800
and do what you want to do.

109
00:06:45,320 --> 00:06:46,320
Li Yan is right.

110
00:06:47,280 --> 00:06:48,840
You really have become much more straightforward.

111
00:06:49,440 --> 00:06:50,840
So what you're after now

112
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:53,680
is to become my wife, the Lady of the City,

113
00:06:54,200 --> 00:06:55,920
isn't it still for the recipe?

114
00:06:56,680 --> 00:06:58,360
I'm also trying to prove

115
00:06:58,680 --> 00:07:01,320
that even a notorious heiress can turn over a new leaf

116
00:07:01,560 --> 00:07:03,160
and one day care for the people like her own children.

117
00:07:03,960 --> 00:07:06,560
This Miss Lin is quite interesting.

118
00:07:10,200 --> 00:07:11,160
Let me walk you back.

119
00:07:11,560 --> 00:07:13,840
Consider it a thank you for bandaging me up

120
00:07:13,840 --> 00:07:15,040
and for drawing the pattern.

121
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:17,200
It's nothing, I can go back myself.

122
00:07:25,320 --> 00:07:25,960
Miss Lin,

123
00:07:26,440 --> 00:07:27,160
Miss Lin,

