00:07:52,080 --> 00:07:53,600
It's so bitter.

126
00:07:56,240 --> 00:07:57,280
Finish this bowl,

127
00:07:58,400 --> 00:07:59,400
and I'll buy you some candy.

128
00:08:01,960 --> 00:08:02,440
Here,

129
00:08:02,720 --> 00:08:03,360
have another sip.

130
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:16,280
Jinjin

131
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:17,600
Are you okay?

132
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:18,240
Wenwen

133
00:08:18,840 --> 00:08:19,560
I'm fine.

134
00:08:20,280 --> 00:08:21,400
No need for you to worry, Commander Li.

135
00:08:21,680 --> 00:08:23,120
I'll take care of Jinjin myself.

136
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:37,040
Jinjin, how are you feeling?

137
00:08:37,040 --> 00:08:38,400
Did you just faint?

138
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:40,320
How did you know?

139
00:08:45,360 --> 00:08:46,440
What are you doing?

140
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:47,240
Don't move.

141
00:08:54,640 --> 00:08:56,320
Your pulse is a bit unsteady.

142
00:08:58,640 --> 00:08:59,240
Wenwen

143
00:08:59,960 --> 00:09:01,440
How do you know everything?

144
00:09:05,320 --> 00:09:07,320
If Wenwen doesn't understand Jinjin,

145
00:09:07,640 --> 00:09:09,080
how can she help her become the city lord's wife?

146
00:09:09,080 --> 00:09:09,920
Don't you think so?

147
00:09:10,200 --> 00:09:12,280
From now on, I'll handle making the medicine.

148
00:09:14,280 --> 00:09:15,000
Well then,

149
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:17,080
I'll go check out the kitchen first.

150
00:09:17,080 --> 00:09:18,080
Get familiar with the place.

151
00:09:18,840 --> 00:09:20,080
Thank you, Wenwen.

152
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:28,280
I took some medicine.

153
00:09:28,280 --> 00:09:29,160
How are you feeling now?

154
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:32,200
Much better.

155
00:09:36,720 --> 00:09:37,800
What about today?

156
00:09:38,480 --> 00:09:39,920
