157
00:09:42,160 --> 00:09:42,640
No.

158
00:09:42,840 --> 00:09:43,360
What are you going to do?

159
00:09:44,360 --> 00:09:45,440
I need to get up quickly.

160
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:47,200
From yesterday to today,

161
00:09:47,440 --> 00:09:48,920
I've already wasted a whole day.

162
00:09:49,640 --> 00:09:50,920
I need to hurry and investigate the case.

163
00:09:51,440 --> 00:09:53,000
Lin Qianjin, come out here!

164
00:09:54,560 --> 00:09:55,280
Brother Li Yan

165
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:57,080
Why are you taking care of this woman?

166
00:10:00,640 --> 00:10:01,920
Changle, you're so willful.

167
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:04,000
You've learned to show up uninvited now.

168
00:10:04,480 --> 00:10:05,640
Then when you went to my place,

169
00:10:05,640 --> 00:10:07,000
and did those sneaky things,

170
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:08,360
did you let me know?

171
00:10:09,640 --> 00:10:11,200
You poisoner!

172
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:11,800
I—

173
00:10:11,800 --> 00:10:13,200
You're the real poisoner!

174
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:13,920
Changle.

175
00:10:14,360 --> 00:10:14,920
Come here.

176
00:10:15,920 --> 00:10:16,440
Changle.

177
00:10:16,840 --> 00:10:17,640
Tell me the truth.

178
00:10:18,200 --> 00:10:19,840
Did you secretly keep any night begonia or not?

179
00:10:21,720 --> 00:10:22,440
I...

180
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:23,640
Changle.

181
00:10:24,840 --> 00:10:26,200
You must tell the truth.

182
00:10:26,720 --> 00:10:28,920
This concerns Princess Liuyun's life.

183
00:10:29,560 --> 00:10:30,360
Brother Liyan,

184
00:10:31,080 --> 00:10:32,280
I do have night begonia,

185
00:10:32,440 --> 00:10:32,920
but—

186
00:10:33,480 --> 00:10:35,560
I used it to make the "Begonia Mystery,"

187
00:10:35,560 --> 00:10:36,280
which is for skincare.

188
00:10:36,280 --> 00:10:38,840
If you don't believe me, come back to my residence and check.

189
00:10:39,440 --> 00:10:40,360
I heard that night begonia

190
00:10:40,360 --> 00:10:41,920
can be made into excellent skincare products.

191
00:10:41,920 --> 00:10:43,640
After using it, your skin becomes smooth as jade.

192
00:10:45,560 --> 00:10:47,360
The princess asked me to buy a tael or two of night begonia.

193
00:10:47,360 --> 00:10:48,560
It's all here.

194
00:10:49,200 --> 00:10:51,280
Weren't you going to make the "Begonia Mystery"?

195
00:10:52,440 --> 00:10:54,160
The process for "Begonia Mystery" is complicated.

196
00:10:54,360 --> 00:10:55,720
I haven't learned it yet.

197
00:10:55,720 --> 00:10:56,440
I'm afraid of ruining it.

198
00:10:56,920 --> 00:10:58,160
So I haven't used the night begonia yet.

199
00:10:58,800 --> 00:10:59,920
How can I be sure

200
00:11:00,200 --> 00:11:01,280
that this is really a tael?

201
00:11:02,000 --> 00:11:03,800
Xiang'er, bring the scale.

202
00:11:28,040 --> 00:11:28,920
Seven qian

203
00:11:30,040 --> 00:11:31,160
Then we're still short three qian.

204
00:11:32,080 --> 00:11:33,320
Still missing three qian.

205
00:11:33,760 --> 00:11:35,320
Didn't you say you didn't make the Haitang Mystery?

206
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:37,640
Then it seems you poisoned Liuyun.

207
00:11:39,320 --> 00:11:39,880
Princess

208
00:11:40,560 --> 00:11:41,200
Is that true?

209
00:11:41,480 --> 00:11:42,280
I didn't.

210
00:11:42,600 --> 00:11:44,480
Li Yan, even you don't believe me?

211
00:11:45,280 --> 00:11:45,880
Then tell me,

212
00:11:46,320 --> 00:11:47,200
these missing three qian,

213
00:11:47,720 --> 00:11:48,760
what did you do with them?

214
00:11:49,720 --> 00:11:50,160
I...

215
00:11:50,760 --> 00:11:51,360
See? See?

216
00:11:51,600 --> 00:11:52,360
You can't explain it, can you?

217
00:11:53,160 --> 00:11:54,480
You, a dignified princess,

218
00:11:54,600 --> 00:11:55,760
actually poisoned Liuyun,

219
00:11:56,040 --> 00:11:57,480
and tried to frame me for it.

220
00:11:58,000 --> 00:11:58,480
Let's go.

221
00:11:58,680 --> 00:11:59,640
You're coming with me to see the city lord.

222
00:11:59,840 --> 00:12:01,040
I want to see what the city lord has to say.

223
00:12:01,040 --> 00:12:01,640
Let go! I didn't poison anyone!

224
00:12:01,640 --> 00:12:02,080
I remember now!

225
00:12:02,320 --> 00:12:04,320
Princess, Miss Lin, Commander Li

226
00:12:04,320 --> 00:12:05,160
