233
00:12:33,320 --> 00:12:36,040
I once put three qian of night begonia in Your Highness's sachet.

234
00:12:36,600 --> 00:12:37,600
Enough, Xiang'er.

235
00:12:39,000 --> 00:12:39,760
Miss Lin.

236
00:12:40,320 --> 00:12:41,160
I now suspect

237
00:12:41,160 --> 00:12:43,320
that you are the one who poisoned Princess Liuyun.

238
00:12:43,920 --> 00:12:46,280
You were so eager to accuse me just now.

239
00:12:46,480 --> 00:12:48,560
It seems to me you just want a scapegoat.

240
00:12:48,560 --> 00:12:49,360
to help you escape blame.

241
00:12:49,360 --> 00:12:49,720
That's right.

242
00:12:49,760 --> 00:12:50,160
I...

243
00:12:50,560 --> 00:12:51,320
I'm not.

244
00:12:51,720 --> 00:12:53,280
You haven't cleared your own name.

245
00:12:53,280 --> 00:12:54,360
And you want to drag me down with you.

246
00:12:54,920 --> 00:12:55,720
I didn't!

247
00:12:55,720 --> 00:12:57,560
Brother Li Yan, you saw that, right?

248
00:12:58,000 --> 00:12:58,880
This vicious woman

249
00:12:58,880 --> 00:13:00,160
has shown her true colors so quickly.

250
00:13:00,640 --> 00:13:02,280
I don't want to stay with her even a moment longer.

251
00:13:02,480 --> 00:13:03,560
Xiang'er, see the guest out.

252
00:13:07,280 --> 00:13:08,480
Miss Lin, please.

253
00:13:12,160 --> 00:13:12,640
I...

254
00:13:17,040 --> 00:13:18,160
Brother Li Yan.

255
00:13:18,600 --> 00:13:20,480
I've already had good food and wine prepared.

256
00:13:20,720 --> 00:13:22,040
Please stay and eat with me.

257
00:13:30,440 --> 00:13:30,840
Miss Lin, what's wrong?

258
00:13:30,840 --> 00:13:31,200
Wait.

259
00:13:31,800 --> 00:13:32,880
Don't fall here.

260
00:13:33,920 --> 00:13:34,600
Brother Li Yan.

261
00:13:35,200 --> 00:13:35,640
Miss.

262
00:13:35,640 --> 00:13:36,160
Miss Lin.

263
00:13:36,720 --> 00:13:37,240
Miss.

264
00:13:39,120 --> 00:13:40,920
The city lord ordered me to protect Miss Lin for seven days.

265
00:13:41,520 --> 00:13:42,800
Then I won't stay, Your Highness.

266
00:13:49,640 --> 00:13:50,880
